    {
      "label": "Content description",
      "value": "Recto: The sender describes someone as being knowledgeable about something (l. 2). He also mentions that he has made a payment (l. 6). The weekday Sunday (l. 5) is mentioned as well as a person named Maym\u016bn (l. 7)\n\u00a0\nVerso: Note starting with the basmala and referring to loads (l. 1), protection and possibly payments (l. 3)."
